text: Pogonocherus jaekeli is an extinct species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae, that existed during the Lower Oligocene. It was described by Zang in 1905.BioLib.cz - Pogonocherus jaekeli. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1905
title: Pogonocherus jaekeli
